px;\">$&nbsp;cd&nbsp;test<\/p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">2) \u521d\u59cb\u5316<\/p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">$&nbsp;git&nbsp;init<\/p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">3) \u521b\u5efahello.md\u6587\u4ef6<\/p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">$&nbsp;echo&nbsp;&quot;\u8fd9\u662f\u4e00\u6b21\u6d4b\u8bd5test&nbsp;ssh&nbsp;key&quot;&nbsp;&gt;&nbsp;hello.md<\/p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">4) \u63d0\u4ea4\u5230\u672c\u5730<\/p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\u82e5\u51fa\u73b0\u5982\u4e0awarning\u63d0\u793a\u5219\u91cd\u65b0\u63d0\u4ea4\u4e00\u6b21\u5373\u53ef\u3002<\/p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">$&nbsp;git&nbsp;add&nbsp;.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;#\u63d0\u4ea4\u5f53\u524d\u76ee\u5f55\u4e0b\u6240\u4ee5\u6587\u4ef6<\/p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">$&nbsp;git&nbsp;commit&nbsp;-m&nbsp;&quot;add&nbsp;hello.md&quot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;#\u63d0\u4ea4\u8bb0\u5f55\u8bf4\u660e&nbsp;<\/p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">5) \u63d0\u4ea4\u5230github<\/p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">$&nbsp;git&nbsp;remote&nbsp;add&nbsp;origin&nbsp;\u2018\u7c98\u8d34\u590d\u5236test&nbsp;ssh&nbsp;key\u7684ssh\u8def\u5f84\u2019&nbsp;&nbsp;#<\/p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">$&nbsp;git&nbsp;push&nbsp;-u&nbsp;origin&nbsp;master<\/p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Enter&nbsp;passphrase&nbsp;for&nbsp;key&nbsp;&#39;\/c\/Users\/hgpin_000\/.ssh\/id_rsa&#39;:&nbsp;&nbsp;#ssh&nbsp;key\u8bbe\u7f6e\u5bc6\u7801\u6545\u6b64\u9700\u8981\u8f93\u5165\u5bc6\u7801<\/p><\/div><div class=\"content-list-media\"><div class=\"content-list-image clearfix\" style=\"zoom: 1; position: relative; padding: 10px 0px;\"><a class=\"exp-image-wrape